This is designed to be a place for me to put various tools that I find helpful
to have when working with aspell.  Depending on how annoyed I get with aspell,
the size of this repository might become larger or smaller.

As a usage note, since this repository starts with "--", if you wish to
interact with it easily on *nix, you might want to consider the following:

  $ alias cd="cd --"

so that you can avoid typing "cd -- --aspell" or "cd ./--aspell" every time
you want to use it.
